title: Yummba
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Buffet, Fast food, Take-out, Middle Eastern
description: Vegetarian fast food cafe located under the cinemas in the main food court of the Bondi Junction Westfield Plaza Shopping Centre. Serves falafels, pita bread, dips, and salads which, according to the staff, are all vegan. The bagels, however, contain egg and some platters come with a hard boiled egg.
